acm.util

Class PatchingClassLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.ClassLoader
      • acm.util.PatchingClassLoader

  • public class PatchingClassLoader
extends ClassLoader
    A ClassLoader that allows you to patch what the superclass is for an existing class as it is loaded. This is primarily used to hot-patch ConsolePrograms to be CommandLinePrograms when run in a non-graphical setting.
